    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Horde is Coming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They will arrive by nightfall, and you are woefully unprepared. With any luck, you'll make it out of this alive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore your Surroundings</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760710/extras/057b85c4205eee5b126311220f85f35e.avif?t=1754889002\" width=1600 height=898 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With 7 unique locations, you must scour all of them to prepare for the oncoming horde.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find and Craft Equipment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the items you find and combine them together to create useful tools and traps.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Watch the Clock</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760710/extras/688b056b2a460487a0f2b3d4832656a9.avif?t=1754889002\" width=394 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every action costs valuable time. With only one day, you must use it wisely.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Prepare your Base</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760710/extras/7007e09b382e29f8cddd0a19de701b79.avif?t=1754889002\" width=1600 height=902 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your hideout could use a few touch-ups. However, you'll need to find the right equipment for the job.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive the Dawn</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the right preparations, you may be able to fend off the horde and survive another day.</p>",
